<main style="max-width:900px;margin:auto;padding:2rem;">
  <h2>Macroeconomic & Data Science Pipeline</h2>

  <p>
    A complete macro-forecasting pipeline that integrates economic time-series modelling with machine learning.
    The workflow includes unit-root testing, lag creation, feature engineering, ARIMA forecasting, OLS estimation,
    and XGBoost modelling.
  </p>

  <p>
    This project shows how economists and data scientists combine theory-based methods with ML flexibility to build
    scalable forecasting systems used in policy research and investment teams.
  </p>

